about Gauri's marriage too.

284
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,080
Did you talk to anybody?

285
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:21,240
Makhan Lal.
- The one who reads the newspaper.

286
00:17:21,320 --> 00:17:23,520
