"I don't know your name."

1168
01:08:28,000 --> 01:08:32,000
"You don't know my name."

1169
01:08:35,720 --> 01:08:37,560
Stop..
- No one will move.

1170
01:08:37,640 --> 01:08:39,280
You all are arrested.

1171
01:08:41,240 --> 01:08:45,200
To pay my exam fees, I
would work at that dirty hotel.

1172
01:08:46,000 --> 01:08:47,560
I would get Rs.5 daily.

1173
01:08:48,360 --> 01:08:49,720
But I didn't know.

1174
01:08:50,320 --> 01:08:52,120
That not only the
destination has to be sacred..

1175
01:08:52,560 --> 01:08:54,000
In fact, the way to
reach that destination..

1176
01:08:54,080 --> 01:08:55,480
..should be sacred too.

1177
01:08:57,000 --> 01:08:58,560
I received the punishment of my sin.

1178
01:08:59,200 --> 01:09:01,360
I had to spend one night
at the police station.

1179
01:09:02,280 --> 01:09:04,280
But on the second day,
when the police came to know..

1180
01:09:04,720 --> 01:09:06,360
..that I have no
relation with that group.

1181
01:09:06,640 --> 01:09:07,760
..they released me.

1182
01:09:08,440 --> 01:09:10,240
Father, now you only tell me.

1183
01:09:10,440 --> 01:09:12,720
How would I have said all
these things in front of them?

1184
01:09:13,080 --> 01:09:15,520
Anyway, they already
see me with hatred.

1185
01:09:16,000 --> 01:09:17,440
If they came know..

1186
01:09:17,520 --> 01:09:19,480
..that I have spent one
night at the police station..

1187
01:09:19,800 --> 01:09:22,160
..they would have kicked
my out of this locality.

1188
01:09:22,400 --> 01:09:23,600
Then where would I have gone?

1189
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:29,400
Bhola, forget the old
things like a dreadful dream.

1190
01:09:30,200 --> 01:09:31,360
Even I'll forget everything.

1191
01:09:31,640 --> 01:09:35,000
Oh, yes, Bhola. You need
Rs.50 for fees. Right? - Yes.

1192
01:09:35,800 --> 01:09:36,880
Take it from me tomorrow.

1193
01:09:37,080 --> 01:09:38,160
Oh, Father.

1194
01:09:38,240 --> 01:09:39,320
Go. Go, my dear, go.

1195
01:09:44,720 --> 01:09:50,400
"Come on, my songs are calling you."

1196
01:09:50,480 --> 01:09:55,720
"My songs. Oh, my beloved."

1197
01:09:56,000 --> 01:09:58,600
"Oh, my beloved."

1198
01:09:58,800 --> 01:10:04,080
"Come on, my songs are calling you."

1199
01:10:04,720 --> 01:10:06,720
Who is it?
- Gauri.

1200
01:10:07,600 --> 01:10:09,120
Why did you call me here?

1201
01:10:09,520 --> 01:10:12,080
Please sit.
- No. I won't sit.

1202
01:10:12,640 --> 01:10:14,360
All right. Shall we talk something?

1203
01:10:16,600 --> 01:10:19,040
Ms. Gauri, I am feeling scared.

1204
01:10:19,360 --> 01:10:20,440
And you?
- No.

1205
01:10:29,640 --> 01:10:31,160
It's useless to sit
silently this way.

1206
01:10:31,240 --> 01:10:33,440
Oh, yes. But what
should I say after all?

1207
01:10:33,720 --> 01:10:35,560
Anything.
- Anything?

1208
01:10:35,800 --> 01:10:36,880
Yes.

1209
01:10:37,320 --> 01:10:38,480
So, tell me how is life?

1210
01:10:39,000 --> 01:10:40,080
Are you all right?

1211
01:10:40,360 --> 01:10:41,560
Are these any talks?

1212
01:10:41,640 --> 01:10:42,720
Then is this mourning?

1213
01:10:43,000 --> 01:10:44,800
Bhola, listen, until
you won't speak to me..

1214
01:10:44,880 --> 01:10:46,000
..I won't go.

1215
01:10:46,080 --> 01:10:47,880
Now, what should I say?

1216
01:10:48,760 --> 01:10:53,120
Oh, yes. You know Mogul
King Akbar, right? - Yes.

1217
01:10:53,200 --> 01:10:54,720
What yes? Say that he is there.

1218
01:10:54,800 --> 01:10:56,080
Hey, dear, he was there.

1219
01:10:56,400 --> 01:10:59,640
At his time, Mogul
Kingdom progressed a lot.

1220
01:11:00,000 --> 01:11:02,000
He was very successful in
bringing good thoughts..

1221
01:11:02,080 --> 01:11:04,200
..and a change in the
hearts of the people.

1222
01:11:04,640 --> 01:11:05,720
Do you know that?

1223
01:11:05,800 --> 01:11:07,440
This is wrong.
- This is wrong?

1224
01:11:07,520 --> 01:11:09,200
Hey, all this is written in History.

1225
01:11:09,280 --> 01:11:10,640
If you want then you can read it.

1226
01:11:10,720 --> 01:11:12,480
No, Bhola, I am not telling that.

1227
01:11:12,560 --> 01:11:15,480
I am saying it's wrong
that you call me so formally.

1228
01:11:15,560 --> 01:11:18,040
Then? What should I call you?

1229
01:11:18,200 --> 01:11:20,200
Casually. Even I'll
call you casually.

1230
01:11:20,280 --> 01:11:21,360
You also call me casually.

1231
01:11:21,640 --> 01:11:24,600
All right. If you wish,
I'll call you casually.

1232
01:11:25,000 --> 01:11:29,080
You.. no.. Gauri,
don't you feel sleepy?

1233
01:11:30,240 --> 01:11:31,320
How will I?

1234
01:11:31,640 --> 01:11:33,200
They called you a thief.

1235
01:11:33,360 --> 01:11:35,000
They scolded and thrashed you.

1236
01:11:36,000 --> 01:11:38,760
Gauri, you worry so much about me?

1237
01:11:40,720 --> 01:11:42,600
The bell rang. I am going.

1238
01:11:42,760 --> 01:11:45,560
Bell? - Yes. You know
our grandfather who coughs.

1239
01:11:45,640 --> 01:11:47,760
If he coughs in the morning,
it's 9 o'clock.

1240
01:11:47,840 --> 01:11:50,200
If he coughs in the evening,
think its 6 o'clock.

1241
01:11:50,280 --> 01:11:52,440
If he coughs at night then
think its 11 o'clock. - Yes.

1242
01:11:52,520 --> 01:11:53,720
He is a clock for me.

1243
01:11:53,800 --> 01:11:55,560
I have to feed medicines to him.
- I am going.

1244
01:11:55,640 --> 01:11:56,720
Coming, Grandfather.

1245
01:12:32,000 --> 01:12:33,080
Who is it? Oh.

1246
01:12:34,800 --> 01:12:36,400
Mr. Mohan. You?

1247
01:12:37,400 --> 01:12:40,000
What's that?

1248
01:12:41,320 --> 01:12:42,480
This shirt belongs to Mr. Jeevan.

1249
01:12:43,160 --> 01:12:44,880
It's not good to steal, Mr. Mohan.

1250
01:12:45,000 --> 01:12:46,200
Speak softly, Bhola.
Someone might hear.

1251
01:12:46,440 --> 01:12:48,320
Not even a beggar
does such filthy things.

1252
01:12:48,400 --> 01:12:50,280
But I am doing it since long.
- What are you blabbering?

1253
01:12:50,720 --> 01:12:52,000
Its better that I saw
you committing the robbery.

1254
01:12:52,080 --> 01:12:53,160
What if someone else had seen you?

1255
01:12:55,320 --> 01:12:58,000
I didn't just watch.
I have heard too.

1256
01:12:58,480 --> 01:12:59,560
You wretched thief.

1257
01:12:59,800 --> 01:13:02,000
You have committed all the
thefts of this locality.

1258
01:13:02,480 --> 01:13:05,800
To defame me, you came
from Agra till here.

1259
01:13:05,880 --> 01:13:07,080
That too by Punjab mail.

1260
01:13:08,280 --> 01:13:11,200
It's good, Bhola,
that you caught him.

1261
01:13:11,480 --> 01:13:14,520
Otherwise, today, I had
been humiliated a lot.

1262
01:13:15,200 --> 01:13:17,000
Please do one more favour, Bhola.

1263
01:13:17,160 --> 01:13:19,880
Never reveal this
rogue's secret to anyone.

1264
01:13:20,240 --> 01:13:22,280
And if necessary, then say..

1265
01:13:22,360 --> 01:13:24,000
You have committed the robbery.

1266
01:13:24,080 --> 01:13:26,000
What are you saying, Mother?

1267
01:13:26,360 --> 01:13:28,560
I can take as many
allegations like a fool.

1268
01:13:28,720 --> 01:13:30,480
But the burden of a
thief's allegation..

1269
01:13:31,000 --> 01:13:32,640
I can't bear to take it at all.

1270
01:13:33,640 --> 01:13:39,000
My dear, not me but a mother..

1271
01:13:39,080 --> 01:13:41,640
..is pleading to her son.

1272
01:13:42,320 --> 01:13:43,720
You don't know, Bhola.

1273
01:13:44,000 --> 01:13:47,600
What can't a son do for his mother?
- Mother.

1274
01:13:47,760 --> 01:13:49,000
You call me mother, right?
- Yes.

1275
01:13:49,080 --> 01:13:50,800
Then take this. Before
anyone comes to know..

1276
01:13:50,880 --> 01:13:53,560
..go and throw these shirts
back there. - Mother. Mother.

1277
01:13:54,880 --> 01:13:58,080
Wicked man. You
cheated the one who fed you.

1278
01:13:58,160 --> 01:13:59,640
Look everyone, look.

1279
01:13:59,720 --> 01:14:03,000
Today, my brother Mohan has
caught this thief red-handed.

1280
01:14:03,080 --> 01:14:04,720
My brother Mohan has caught him.

1281
01:14:04,800 --> 01:14:06,360
Come on, speak up.
What will you say now?

1282
01:14:06,440 --> 01:14:08,240
I am not a thief. I
didn't commit the robbery.

1283
01:14:08,320 --> 01:14:09,880
Mother.
- Hey, you thief.

1284
01:14:12,000 --> 01:14:13,080
What is this new matter?

1285
01:14:13,160 --> 01:14:15,000
Yes, yes. These are new shirts.

1286
01:14:15,120 --> 01:14:16,560
Bhola have stolen
these shirts from upstairs.

1287
01:14:16,640 --> 01:14:19,000
Hey? These are my brother's shirts.

1288
01:14:19,280 --> 01:14:22,200
This wretched one cheats
the ones who feed him.

1289
01:14:22,720 --> 01:14:24,560
Father..
- Bhola, did you forget?

1290
01:14:24,640 --> 01:14:26,080
Today, wheat is so expensive.

1291
01:14:26,160 --> 01:14:27,440
Vegetables are so costly.

1292
01:14:27,520 --> 01:14:30,360
Even then I feed you so lovingly.

1293
01:14:30,560 --> 01:14:32,000
Tell the truth,
Bhola. What's the matter?

1294
01:14:32,080 --> 01:14:34,240
Father..
- Bhola, I feed you. Right?

1295
01:14:34,480 --> 01:14:35,880
I am your mother. Right?

1296
01:14:36,080 --> 01:14:38,000
Then tell the truth, dear.
- Tell the truth.

1297
01:14:38,080 --> 01:14:39,800
Your mother is asking you.

1298
01:14:39,880 --> 01:14:41,200
Tell me, Bhola. What's the matter?

1299
01:14:41,280 --> 01:14:42,520
I am your mother, Bhola.

1300
01:14:46,800 --> 01:14:49,520
These shirts.. I have
stolen these shirts.

1301
01:14:51,520 --> 01:14:55,720
Bhola, have you really
stolen these shirts? Yes?

1302
01:14:56,320 --> 01:14:58,160
Yes. I picked them up by mistake.

1303
01:14:58,280 --> 01:15:02,480
This means that
silver glass, gold chain..

1304
01:15:02,560 --> 01:15:04,000
..that nose ring, that cash.

1305
01:15:04,080 --> 01:15:05,160
You have stolen everything?

1306
01:15:05,640 --> 01:15:07,520
You forget to mention
about brother's watch.

1307
01:15:13,720 --> 01:15:16,000
Did you see? Your
darling Bhola has been caught..

1308
01:15:16,080 --> 01:15:17,360
..stealing in our house today.

1309
01:15:17,480 --> 01:15:19,400
You were praising
Bhola a lot that day.

1310
01:15:19,720 --> 01:15:21,000
You were threatening everyone.

1311
01:15:21,080 --> 01:15:22,160
What happened now?
- Why are you dumbstruck?

1312
01:15:30,720 --> 01:15:32,080
A thief. Hundred percent, a thief.

1313
01:15:36,000 --> 01:15:40,000
Bhola, I can't
believe in my dreams..

1314
01:15:40,080 --> 01:15:41,160
..that you are a thief.

1315
01:15:42,000 --> 01:15:44,720
Tell me, did you
steal or not? Tell me.

1316
01:15:45,640 --> 01:15:46,880
Say that you didn't
commit the robbery.

1317
01:15:48,280 --> 01:15:51,000
Say that you didn't steal..

1318
01:15:52,320 --> 01:15:55,080
Brother, please forgive me.

1319
01:15:56,160 --> 01:15:57,240
I committed a mistake.

1320
01:15:57,640 --> 01:15:58,720
I committed a mistake.

1321
01:15:58,800 --> 01:16:00,000
So, you committed a mistake
- Yes.

1322
01:16:03,000 --> 01:16:04,080
You thief..

1323
01:16:04,720 --> 01:16:05,800
Rogue.

1324
01:16:06,800 --> 01:16:09,040
I was so proud of you.

1325
01:16:10,000 --> 01:16:12,000
I would walk with pride.

1326
01:16:13,360 --> 01:16:18,560
And today? Today,
you have humiliated me.

1327
01:16:19,480 --> 01:16:22,000
You fool. Shame on you.

1328
01:16:24,000 --> 01:16:25,880
Sher Singh, this is
an incomplete issue.

1329
01:16:27,000 --> 01:16:28,240
I will complete it.

1330
01:16:29,000 --> 01:16:30,320
I will teach him a lesson.

1331
01:16:31,160 --> 01:16:32,360
Forget it, Mr. Manohar Lal.

1332
01:16:32,440 --> 01:16:33,680
What if anything goes wrong?

1333
01:16:33,760 --> 01:16:35,320
Nothing will go wrong.

1334
01:16:35,400 --> 01:16:36,560
I will make everything fine.

1335
01:16:37,320 --> 01:16:39,120
I have controlled it for many days.

1336
01:16:40,000 --> 01:16:44,880
Gauri's mother,
first, you fed him. - Yes.

1337
01:16:45,400 --> 01:16:47,080
You fed him expensive vegetables.

1338
01:16:48,000 --> 01:16:49,520
Even then he stole the shirts.

1339
01:16:50,280 --> 01:16:53,320
You rogue, fool, cheat.

1340
01:16:53,400 --> 01:16:55,160
Hey? Brother-in-law.
Brother-in-law, what are you doing?

1341
01:16:55,240 --> 01:16:57,480
Sister. Sister. Please save me.
- Save me, Sister.

1342
01:16:57,560 --> 01:16:58,640
Brother-in-law.
Brother-in-law, what are you doing?

1343
01:16:58,720 --> 01:17:00,200
What are you doing? - So,
Bhola committed the robbery, right?

1344
01:17:00,440 --> 01:17:02,440
You all still didn't understand

1345
01:17:02,640 --> 01:17:03,760
I will explain to everyone.

1346
01:17:04,080 --> 01:17:05,560
Here is all the stolen stuff.

1347
01:17:05,640 --> 01:17:07,800
And my uncle Mohan has
done this great thing.

1348
01:17:08,000 --> 01:17:10,640
Oh, God. Did Mohan
commit this robbery then?

1349
01:17:10,800 --> 01:17:13,480
He stole all the things and
kept them in his suitcase.

1350
01:17:13,640 --> 01:17:16,120
Here. Your silver glass.
- The second glass?

1351
01:17:16,480 --> 01:17:19,240
Here.
- My nose ring? - It's here.

1352
01:17:19,400 --> 01:17:22,200
And my gold chain?
- Here. - Thank you.

1353
01:17:23,040 --> 01:17:27,000
Brother Sher Singh.
Brother Sher Singh.

1354
01:17:27,640 --> 01:17:28,880
Brother Sher Singh.
- Yes?

1355
01:17:29,320 --> 01:17:30,400
Your watch.

1356
01:17:31,120 --> 01:17:32,200
Please take it.

1357
01:17:32,280 --> 01:17:35,080
Now, everyone has got
their stuff. Now, go.

1358
01:17:35,160 --> 01:17:36,320
Why are you all standing here?
- Go from here.

1359
01:17:36,400 --> 01:17:38,240
Oh, yes. Come on,
everyone, go to their houses.

1360
01:17:38,320 --> 01:17:39,440
Mother has become very angry.

1361
01:17:42,080 --> 01:17:43,200
It's my brother's shirt.

1362
01:17:44,720 --> 01:17:46,200
Come on, go inside. Go now.

1363
01:17:47,160 --> 01:17:50,160
To defame me, this thief
came from Agra to Mumbai.

1364
01:17:50,480 --> 01:17:52,560
Don't consider this
wretched man as my wife's brother.

1365
01:17:52,640 --> 01:17:54,640
Call the police. Hand
him over to the police.

1366
01:17:54,720 --> 01:17:56,320
Brother-in-law, please forgive me.

1367
01:17:56,400 --> 01:17:59,200
So, I should forgive you?
- Father, please forgive Mr. Mohan.

1368
01:18:00,000 --> 01:18:02,080
Brother Bhola, please forgive me.

1369
01:18:02,160 --> 01:18:03,440
I will never commit
robbery in my life again.

1370
01:18:03,520 --> 01:18:05,800
All right. All right,
first, you get out of the house.

1371
01:18:05,880 --> 01:18:07,000
Get out. Come on, go now.

1372
01:18:41,160 --> 01:18:44,520
Oh, yes, Brother. Brother,
I just forgot to tell you.

1373
01:18:44,880 --> 01:18:47,200
Today, I ate food at the
Punjabi hotel, Sher-e-Punjab.

1374
01:18:47,400 --> 01:18:48,440
Chana Bhaturas (Grams
and fried flatbread).

1375
01:18:48,520 --> 01:18:49,600
They were very tasty.

1376
01:18:50,000 --> 01:18:53,280
Brother. Brother, please
tell me how they are prepared.

1377
01:18:53,800 --> 01:18:59,000
Bhola, you think by talking
about these things, you'll..

1378
01:19:00,280 --> 01:19:04,320
No. No. You didn't eat
food from a Punjabi hotel.

1379
01:19:04,520 --> 01:19:07,200
You have been
slapped by a Punjabi man.

1380
01:19:07,720 --> 01:19:09,480
I am very ashamed.

1381
01:19:09,720 --> 01:19:12,000
Hey, listen, I can't face you.

1382
01:19:12,560 --> 01:19:13,720
Don't say that, Brother.

1383
01:19:14,400 --> 01:19:16,800
I don't regret being slapped by you.

1384
01:19:18,000 --> 01:19:21,760
I was scared.. What if
our friendship breaks?

1385
01:19:22,760 --> 01:19:25,880
Brother, I can bear
the death of a friend.

1386
01:19:27,000 --> 01:19:29,640
But I can't bear the
death of friendship.

1387
01:19:30,720 --> 01:19:33,480
Bhola, the elders
say the right thing.

1388
01:19:34,280 --> 01:19:35,720
Work in haste, repent at leisure.

1389
01:19:36,600 --> 01:19:39,000
The punishment for
my mistake is this.

1390
01:19:39,880 --> 01:19:44,000
I misunderstood you
because of this watch.

1391
01:19:45,240 --> 01:19:46,600
I am not worth
wearing that wristwatch.

1392
01:19:47,000 --> 01:19:49,000
Here. Here. You wear
this watch on your wrist.

1393
01:19:49,080 --> 01:19:50,440
No, Brother, no.

1394
01:19:51,000 --> 01:19:52,640
You lose it and I get it.

1395
01:19:52,720 --> 01:19:54,640
This is impossible.
- I say, take it. - No, Brother.

1396
01:19:54,720 --> 01:19:55,800
Take it.
- No.

1397
01:19:56,080 --> 01:19:59,000
All right. If this watch
is not on Bhola's wrist..

1398
01:19:59,080 --> 01:20:00,640
..then this watch will be no more.

1399
01:20:02,000 --> 01:20:03,080
Oh, yes.

1400
01:20:04,000 --> 01:20:08,440
Bhola. - Yes? - Do you
remember what I would always say?

1401
01:20:08,760 --> 01:20:11,280
Three things are very
dear to me in this world.

1402
01:20:11,640 --> 01:20:12,720
Yes, Brother.

1403
01:20:13,320 --> 01:20:14,720
Firstly, your mother.
- Yes.

1404
01:20:15,400 --> 01:20:16,800
Secondly, this watch.
- Oh, yes.

1405
01:20:17,360 --> 01:20:18,560
And third one is your intelligence.

1406
01:20:20,720 --> 01:20:23,000
No. No. Not my intelligence.

1407
01:20:24,080 --> 01:20:25,640
Third one is my Bhola.

1408
01:20:26,000 --> 01:20:28,800
Oh, Brother.
- Oh, yes. My pal.

1409
01:20:43,720 --> 01:20:44,800
What is it?

1410
01:20:44,880 --> 01:20:49,000
Come here. Yes.
Wait. Here. Take this.

1411
01:20:49,360 --> 01:20:50,880
What is this?
- A flower braid.

1412
01:20:51,080 --> 01:20:52,440
You always make a hairdo, right?

1413
01:20:52,520 --> 01:20:56,000
So, wear this.
- Why? - I want to see it.

1414
01:20:57,200 --> 01:21:00,160
Seeing your beauty, even
moon will feel ashamed.

1415
01:21:00,800 --> 01:21:05,080
And you? - When moon will
feel ashamed.. I will faint.

1416
01:21:05,480 --> 01:21:08,000
Then I won't wear it.
- No. I was just joking.

1417
01:21:08,080 --> 01:21:09,520
Please wear it.
- All right.

1418
01:21:14,160 --> 01:21:16,880
Bhola.
- Brother Vivek. Please sit.

1419
01:21:17,720 --> 01:21:19,000
I have heard the
people of this locality..

1420
01:21:19,080 --> 01:21:21,520
..alleged you to be a thief
and gave you a lot of respect.

1421
01:21:21,600 --> 01:21:23,200
Yes, but they took that rank back.

1422
01:21:23,360 --> 01:21:24,440
Shall I tell you one thing?

1423
01:21:24,520 --> 01:21:26,480
The people of this
locality don't know your value.

1424
01:21:26,640 --> 01:21:28,080
Only father has guessed you right.

1425
01:21:28,560 --> 01:21:30,560
That's why he brought
books for me to study.

1426
01:21:31,000 --> 01:21:33,240
I can't understand how
to repay his favour.

1427
01:21:33,400 --> 01:21:35,000
You'll get an opportunity soon.

1428
01:21:35,480 --> 01:21:38,880
Father wants you to
marry my sister Shanti.

1429
01:21:41,200 --> 01:21:43,280
My marriage with your father.. No,
I mean with your sister.

1430
01:21:43,360 --> 01:21:44,440
No. What are you saying?

1431
01:21:44,560 --> 01:21:45,640
I am telling the
right thing, Brother.

1432
01:21:45,720 --> 01:21:48,080
And father will come
here to talk about marriage.

1433
01:21:48,160 --> 01:21:50,800
Father? Oh, no. Why is
father going to come here?

1434
01:21:50,880 --> 01:21:52,640
He should have called me there.
I would have come.

1435
01:21:53,320 --> 01:21:55,360
You are getting so uneasy
listening about marriage.

1436
01:21:56,000 --> 01:21:57,080
Be patient, Brother.

1437
01:21:57,280 --> 01:21:59,120
All right. It's time
for father to come.

1438
01:21:59,200 --> 01:22:00,480
I am going.
- All the best.

1439
01:22:08,480 --> 01:22:09,560
Happy marriage.

1440
01:22:10,160 --> 01:22:11,480
Till today, I would think..

1441
01:22:11,560 --> 01:22:14,160
Your professor gives you only books.

1442
01:22:14,480 --> 01:22:16,000
But today, I came to
know he is ready..

1443
01:22:16,080 --> 01:22:18,000
..to give you his daughter too.

1444
01:22:18,400 --> 01:22:19,480
How is the girl?

1445
01:22:19,560 --> 01:22:20,640
When will the marriage take place?

1446
01:22:21,080 --> 01:22:23,640
Gauri, didn't you feel
bad listening to this?

1447
01:22:24,280 --> 01:22:26,800
No.
- Not at all? - No, not at all.

1448
01:22:27,320 --> 01:22:28,640
A marriage is good news.

1449
01:22:28,800 --> 01:22:30,000
Everyone feels happy.

1450
01:22:30,200 --> 01:22:31,400
Why should anyone feel bad?

1451
01:22:31,800 --> 01:22:33,000
It's fine if everyone feels happy.

1452
01:22:33,560 --> 01:22:35,000
But can Gauri also feel happy?

1453
01:22:35,720 --> 01:22:36,880
Why are you asking me this?

1454
01:22:37,080 --> 01:22:42,160
Because.. I.. you..
- Hey? Why are you stammering?

1455
01:22:42,480 --> 01:22:44,000
I thought after
listening that I am..

1456
01:22:44,080 --> 01:22:47,000
..getting married
to some other girl..

1457
01:22:47,080 --> 01:22:48,160
..you will get disheartened.

1458
01:22:51,400 --> 01:22:55,000
Hey Bhola, when father-in-law
is coming to see son-in-law..

1459
01:22:55,080 --> 01:22:57,000
..should the
son-in-law be in this attire?

1460
01:22:57,080 --> 01:22:59,000
You should get ready.

1461
01:22:59,120 --> 01:23:00,200
Understood?

1462
01:23:01,200 --> 01:23:02,280
Here. Take this.

1463
01:23:03,400 --> 01:23:04,480
You had given it, right?

1464
01:23:06,080 --> 01:23:08,160
Gauri.
- Bye.

1465
01:23:08,480 --> 01:23:09,560
Gauri.

1466
01:23:14,000 --> 01:23:16,000
Bhola. Bhola.

1467
01:23:16,280 --> 01:23:17,400
Oh, sir. Greetings, sir.

1468
01:23:17,480 --> 01:23:19,000
How are you, Bhola?
- I am fine. I am fine, sir.

1469
01:23:19,080 --> 01:23:20,160
Please come. Come.

1470
01:23:20,400 --> 01:23:22,000
Sir, where will you sit? I don't
have an appropriate place for you..

1471
01:23:22,080 --> 01:23:24,240
Thank you. Thank you, Bhola.
- Sir, I.. Oh, no.

1472
01:23:24,320 --> 01:23:25,720
Sir, what should I bring for you?

1473
01:23:25,800 --> 01:23:26,880
Chilled tea or hot Cola?

1474
01:23:27,000 --> 01:23:28,080
Thank you, Bhola.

1475
01:23:28,280 --> 01:23:30,800
Bhola, I always ask about you.
- Yes.

