02:08:13,140 --> 02:08:14,380
Mr. Bhola.
- Yes.

2192
02:08:14,740 --> 02:08:18,420
When you read love letters,
your eyes get strained.

2193
02:08:18,540 --> 02:08:21,580
So? - So, I brought
a table lamp for you.

2194
02:08:21,820 --> 02:08:24,980
And look, I even
brought sweet for you.

2195
02:08:25,140 --> 02:08:31,900
I prepared it myself. Your life
will be as sweet as this sweet.

2196
02:08:32,860 --> 02:08:39,580
Mr. Bhola. I was upset to
read your letter last time.

2197
02:08:39,900 --> 02:08:41,460
Please don't feel bad about it.

2198
02:08:41,740 --> 02:08:46,220
But nowadays, I read that
letter 20 times everyday. - Really?

2199
02:08:48,940 --> 02:08:51,700
Mr. Bhola, please don't
look at me in this manner.

2200
02:08:51,780 --> 02:08:53,820
What is the matter?
- I feel shy.

2201
02:08:53,940 --> 02:08:55,980
When you see a young man,
you forget everything.

2202
02:08:56,220 --> 02:08:59,300
You saw this young man
and came here to him.

2203
02:08:59,380 --> 02:09:00,900
No one is there to look after you.

2204
02:09:02,300 --> 02:09:03,460
Bhola.
- Yes, Mother.

2205
02:09:03,580 --> 02:09:05,100
I brought a cup of tea for you.

2206
02:09:05,580 --> 02:09:08,420
Why have you come here
now?-Shut up. I'm Bhola's friend.

2207
02:09:09,900 --> 02:09:11,420
Bhola.
- Uncle.

2208
02:09:11,740 --> 02:09:13,420
Look, what I've brought for you.

2209
02:09:13,900 --> 02:09:15,100
A fan.

2210
02:09:15,580 --> 02:09:19,260
Switch it on and take good rest.

2211
02:09:19,380 --> 02:09:20,460
Take it. Be careful.

2212
02:09:21,420 --> 02:09:23,700
It is very heavy. It is very costly.

2213
02:09:26,260 --> 02:09:27,700
Singapore.

2214
02:09:27,780 --> 02:09:28,860
Uncle, what about Singapore?

2215
02:09:28,980 --> 02:09:31,140
Singapore. My dear.

2216
02:09:32,460 --> 02:09:34,220
Bhola, the tea is getting cold.

2217
02:09:34,500 --> 02:09:37,500
Drink it.
- Just food is not enough.

2218
02:09:37,580 --> 02:09:39,700
Mr. Bhola is a graduate, but
he has to sleep on the ground.

2219
02:09:39,820 --> 02:09:41,860
Mr. Jeevan, are
you going outstation?

2220
02:09:42,140 --> 02:09:44,460
No, Mr. Bhola, I've
brought this quilt for you.

2221
02:09:44,580 --> 02:09:46,460
Oh.
- So that you can sleep in comfort.

2222
02:09:46,820 --> 02:09:49,420
But Mr. Bhola, I
gave you this quilt.

2223
02:09:49,580 --> 02:09:51,100
I don't want to publicise it.

2224
02:09:51,580 --> 02:09:53,580
Renu. Have you met Mr. Bhola?

2225
02:09:53,700 --> 02:09:56,940
Yes. Renu came and went away.

2226
02:09:57,060 --> 02:09:58,740
Okay. Okay. I'll
take your leave now.

2227
02:09:59,300 --> 02:10:00,580
Drink it, my dear.

2228
02:10:00,700 --> 02:10:04,020
Bhola. Don't drink the tea.
It's not good for your health.

2229
02:10:04,140 --> 02:10:07,820
Drink Horlicks (energy drink).
Here's the health drink. Horlicks.

2230
02:10:10,260 --> 02:10:11,500
And hot water for you.

2231
02:10:12,060 --> 02:10:14,460
Whenever you want, mix it
with Horlicks and drink it.

2232
02:10:14,580 --> 02:10:16,580
Sister, why are you
taking the trouble?

2233
02:10:17,140 --> 02:10:18,740
Bhola has drunk healthy tea.

2234
02:10:19,180 --> 02:10:23,060
Dear Bhola, you should not
take food from any derelict.

2235
02:10:23,340 --> 02:10:26,820
Oh. You call me a derelict.
Are you a queen?

2236
02:10:26,940 --> 02:10:28,700
Yes, I'm a queen.
- Bhola, drink this healthy drink.

2237
02:10:28,820 --> 02:10:30,300
Bhola, don't drink it.
- Bhola, drink it.

2238
02:10:30,460 --> 02:10:35,140
Bhola don't. - Drink it. - No.
- You must drink it. - No.

2239
02:10:35,300 --> 02:10:37,300
Oh.
- Help.

2240
02:10:37,420 --> 02:10:38,500
Bhola can't breathe.

2241
02:10:38,580 --> 02:10:41,700
Bhola can't breathe.
- Bhola can't breathe.

2242
02:10:41,820 --> 02:10:42,900
Give Bhola some water.

2243
02:10:43,020 --> 02:10:46,060
Bhola, have some water. -
Here's the water. - I'm coming, son.

2244
02:10:46,180 --> 02:10:47,860
Water.
- Water.

2245
02:10:49,260 --> 02:10:52,700
Wait, I'll give him.
- I'll give him water.

2246
02:10:52,780 --> 02:10:55,380
Take from me. - I'll give him water.

2247
02:10:55,500 --> 02:10:57,060
Who are you to give water to Bhola?

2248
02:10:57,180 --> 02:10:58,980
Bhola is my son.
- Shut up.

2249
02:10:59,700 --> 02:11:01,580
Don't try to teach me.
- Shut up.

2250
02:11:09,580 --> 02:11:12,340
Why do people fight like animals?

2251
02:11:14,900 --> 02:11:17,820
Hey, what are you
doing inside the house?

2252
02:11:17,980 --> 02:11:20,340
Go out and talk to Bhola.

2253
02:11:20,580 --> 02:11:24,140
But the other day, you said
you'll break my legs if I went out.

2254
02:11:24,260 --> 02:11:27,340
But today, you are asking me
to go out and talk to Bhola.

2255
02:11:27,460 --> 02:11:29,820
You have no sense. You are stupid.

2256
02:11:30,940 --> 02:11:32,020
Am I stupid?

2257
02:11:32,340 --> 02:11:33,580
Will you go or not?

2258
02:11:34,020 --> 02:11:35,500
No. Not at all.

2259
02:11:41,100 --> 02:11:45,580
Hey, Bhola. You have
become a king from a pauper.

2260
02:11:45,700 --> 02:11:46,780
What is the matter?

2261
02:11:47,020 --> 02:11:49,140
Brother, I do not
know what the matter is.

2262
02:11:49,340 --> 02:11:50,940
I only know that I
have become a millionaire.

2263
02:11:51,100 --> 02:11:54,220
Oh. Millionaire?
- Yes. A millionaire.

2264
02:11:54,900 --> 02:11:56,940
Brother, take Rs.50.

2265
02:11:57,460 --> 02:11:58,580
What for?

2266
02:11:59,060 --> 02:12:00,700
Brother, now, your
Bhola is no more a pauper..

2267
02:12:00,780 --> 02:12:02,820
..but he has become wealthy.

2268
02:12:03,300 --> 02:12:05,740
By the way, I have
used your watch a lot.

2269
02:12:05,900 --> 02:12:07,180
Thank you for that.

2270
02:12:07,820 --> 02:12:09,700
Now, I do not want
this watch for free.

2271
02:12:09,820 --> 02:12:11,060
Hey, you son of a millionaire.

2272
02:12:11,300 --> 02:12:13,220
You are weighing a gift
given with love with your money?

2273
02:12:13,380 --> 02:12:15,700
Brother, a person can
buy love, affection..

2274
02:12:15,780 --> 02:12:17,700
..everything with money. Take Rs.50.

2275
02:12:17,820 --> 02:12:19,340
Bhola.
- Keep Rs.50.

2276
02:12:19,580 --> 02:12:21,180
You dare to do this. Crook..

2277
02:12:21,900 --> 02:12:23,460
You crook. You crook.

2278
02:12:25,340 --> 02:12:27,420
Brother, say it. You crook.

2279
02:12:30,140 --> 02:12:31,700
Come on, Brother. Say it.
- I won't say it.

2280
02:12:31,900 --> 02:12:33,700
I understood, you
want to make me angry..

2281
02:12:33,780 --> 02:12:35,700
..and you want me
to say crook.. yes..

2282
02:12:35,780 --> 02:12:39,060
You want me to say that. No,
I will not say that.

2283
02:12:39,180 --> 02:12:40,940
Brother, just once.
- I will never say it.

2284
02:12:41,420 --> 02:12:43,260
Bhola, what is all this?

2285
02:12:43,380 --> 02:12:46,020
Brother, I have become lucky.
I have become a millionaire.

2286
02:12:46,140 --> 02:12:47,820
I have got all the happiness.
- Great. Great.

2287
02:12:48,020 --> 02:12:49,820
But I did not get one thing.
- What is that?

2288
02:12:51,100 --> 02:12:53,060
Sleep. Peaceful sleep.

2289
02:12:53,180 --> 02:12:56,140
Oh, Bhola, this is
the miracle of money.

2290
02:12:56,380 --> 02:12:59,060
When you get money,
you lose your peace.

2291
02:12:59,420 --> 02:13:00,500
You lose your sleep.

2292
02:13:00,740 --> 02:13:03,740
But Brother, these
people are very strange.

2293
02:13:03,860 --> 02:13:06,180
They start hovering around
you once you have money.

2294
02:13:06,340 --> 02:13:08,780
Just see, what all gifts the people
from the shanty have given me.

2295
02:13:08,900 --> 02:13:11,700
It is really surprising. In
one day, all have started..

2296
02:13:11,780 --> 02:13:13,580
..respecting you so much. Wow.

2297
02:13:13,740 --> 02:13:16,900
But Brother, you have
not given me anything. Why?

2298
02:13:17,020 --> 02:13:18,500
Has your father given all this?

2299
02:13:18,580 --> 02:13:20,780
All these gifts are given by me.

2300
02:13:20,900 --> 02:13:22,180
You haven't given me.

2301
02:13:22,300 --> 02:13:23,500
The people from the
shanty have given me.

2302
02:13:23,580 --> 02:13:25,740
That too after seeing the
face of my wealthy father.

2303
02:13:25,860 --> 02:13:27,260
Which wealthy father?

2304
02:13:27,420 --> 02:13:28,500
Brother, even I do not know it.

2305
02:13:28,580 --> 02:13:31,380
But I have heard that he
has come from Singapore.

2306
02:13:31,580 --> 02:13:32,780
He is elegantly dressed up.

2307
02:13:32,900 --> 02:13:34,220
He has come from Singapore.

2308
02:13:34,340 --> 02:13:36,340
He is elegantly dressed up. Wait.

2309
02:13:39,580 --> 02:13:44,740
Bhola, do you know who is he?
- Who is he?

2310
02:13:44,940 --> 02:13:47,020
Your father from Singapore.

2311
02:13:47,500 --> 02:13:49,060
What?
- Yes, Bhola.

2312
02:13:49,380 --> 02:13:51,700
The people who wear a
suit are not usually..

2313
02:13:51,780 --> 02:13:53,740
..the millionaire from Singapore.

2314
02:13:53,940 --> 02:13:55,700
He is not your father
but he is my cleaner..

2315
02:13:55,780 --> 02:13:56,860
My cleaner, Jaggu.

2316
02:13:56,940 --> 02:13:59,140
He plays the role of
Majnu's father in dramas.

2317
02:13:59,260 --> 02:14:00,780
I told him to become
Bhola's father one day.

2318
02:14:00,900 --> 02:14:03,820
I will see who comes to trouble you.

2319
02:14:03,980 --> 02:14:05,060
How did he say it?

2320
02:14:05,460 --> 02:14:08,580
Hey, you. Hey, you
people from the shanty.

2321
02:14:08,860 --> 02:14:12,060
Come out of your rooms.

2322
02:14:12,420 --> 02:14:17,140
Look. Your millionaire
from Singapore has arrived.

2323
02:14:17,420 --> 02:14:19,700
The one who was going
to give all of you..

2324
02:14:19,780 --> 02:14:21,420
..Rs.1 lakh each.

2325
02:14:21,540 --> 02:14:24,300
Come. Come and take Rs.1 lakh.

2326
02:14:24,420 --> 02:14:28,580
Come, Jagya, there are Re.1
notes filled in the truck.

2327
02:14:28,700 --> 02:14:30,340
Come on, Jagya.

2328
02:14:42,900 --> 02:14:45,500
Horlicks gives you more strength.

2329
02:14:45,580 --> 02:14:47,940
Horlicks gives you more strength.

2330
02:14:48,020 --> 02:14:50,140
Horlicks gives you more strength.

2331
02:14:50,300 --> 02:14:51,380
Horlicks..
- Bhola.

2332
02:14:51,700 --> 02:14:53,420
Since the time I have
given you this clock..

2333
02:14:53,500 --> 02:14:56,580
..Jaya.. my wife,
she keeps screaming.

2334
02:14:57,740 --> 02:14:59,180
I will throw this clock on her face.

2335
02:14:59,300 --> 02:15:00,700
Throw it on her face.
- Yes, on her face..

2336
02:15:03,060 --> 02:15:05,220
Beware if you ever
write a love letter to me.

2337
02:15:05,580 --> 02:15:07,500
And you eat sweet free of cost.

2338
02:15:14,900 --> 02:15:17,140
Singapore? Hey, you fraud.

2339
02:15:23,180 --> 02:15:24,580
You are not going anywhere,
are you? - No.

2340
02:15:24,700 --> 02:15:25,980
Then I will take my suitcase away.

2341
02:15:27,740 --> 02:15:30,260
Hey, millionaire. Rubbish.

2342
02:15:33,500 --> 02:15:35,580
Bhola, I am going out of town.

2343
02:15:37,420 --> 02:15:39,740
I am taking away the Horlicks.

2344
02:15:39,820 --> 02:15:41,940
I am taking away the Horlicks.

2345
02:15:42,020 --> 02:15:43,100
Horlicks.

2346
02:15:47,140 --> 02:15:48,580
Get up.

2347
02:15:57,340 --> 02:15:59,300
Gradually, everything disappeared.

2348
02:16:05,340 --> 02:16:08,420
Oh, Bhola. My dear. Get up.

2349
02:16:09,500 --> 02:16:10,580
Tell me, Bhola.

2350
02:16:10,700 --> 02:16:12,020
Where did all these things vanish..

2351
02:16:12,100 --> 02:16:13,180
..the moment I went away?

2352
02:16:13,580 --> 02:16:15,340
They went back where
they had come from.

2353
02:16:15,700 --> 02:16:19,420
Don't worry, look what
I have brought for you.

2354
02:16:19,500 --> 02:16:20,580
A ticket for Delhi.

2355
02:16:21,020 --> 02:16:22,140
Brother, ticket is fine.

2356
02:16:22,940 --> 02:16:24,420
But first, you tell me
why did you play such..

2357
02:16:24,500 --> 02:16:25,580
..a bitter mischief with me?

2358
02:16:25,940 --> 02:16:28,700
Oh, Bhola, not with you.
I played this mischief..

2359
02:16:28,780 --> 02:16:30,580
..with the people from this shanty.

2360
02:16:30,780 --> 02:16:32,260
My dear, this is my principle.

2361
02:16:32,460 --> 02:16:35,900
To lure a greedy person
and make him do your bidding.

2362
02:16:36,180 --> 02:16:38,580
And to fool by falsely praising him.

2363
02:16:39,540 --> 02:16:42,060
This is what an intelligent
person has said, understood?

2364
02:16:42,260 --> 02:16:43,700
I don't want to know anything.

2365
02:16:43,820 --> 02:16:45,700
But first, tell me what
was the necessity to..

2366
02:16:45,780 --> 02:16:46,940
..play this charade with me?

2367
02:16:47,060 --> 02:16:48,260
I did not plan this charade.

2368
02:16:48,500 --> 02:16:49,820
This was planned by Gauri.

2369
02:16:49,900 --> 02:16:51,180
I just supported her.

2370
02:16:51,300 --> 02:16:52,940
Gauri?
- Yes, yes, Gauri.

2371
02:17:00,060 --> 02:17:01,140
Gauri.

2372
02:17:10,820 --> 02:17:15,500
Yes. I wanted to make
you a king for a day.

2373
02:17:15,940 --> 02:17:18,260
I wanted everyone to serve you.

2374
02:17:19,140 --> 02:17:20,820
Brother Sher Khan supported me.

2375
02:17:21,780 --> 02:17:25,020
I wanted to exact revenge.

2376
02:17:25,100 --> 02:17:26,700
I wanted to exact revenge
against each and every person.

2377
02:17:27,420 --> 02:17:29,940
Today, after seeing
everyone was serving you..

2378
02:17:30,940 --> 02:17:33,820
I realised that the
world is made up of fools.

2379
02:17:35,300 --> 02:17:37,700
If I would have known
this earlier then I..

2380
02:17:37,780 --> 02:17:42,140
..I would have never come out
from the mental asylum. Never.

2381
02:17:42,700 --> 02:17:45,780
Gauri, you did the right thing.
Absolutely the right thing.

2382
02:17:49,340 --> 02:17:51,780
Okay, so you have taken revenge.

2383
02:17:52,140 --> 02:17:53,220
What?

2384
02:17:56,500 --> 02:17:59,380
Look how they fooled us?
- Yes.

2385
02:17:59,500 --> 02:18:01,060
I will teach her a lesson.

2386
02:18:01,180 --> 02:18:03,020
Aunt. Come out.

2387
02:18:03,140 --> 02:18:04,780
Why are you calling out to aunt?

2388
02:18:04,900 --> 02:18:06,260
She too is deceived.

2389
02:18:06,380 --> 02:18:08,580
You are all the same. Just the same.

2390
02:18:08,940 --> 02:18:11,380
Hey, you. You did all this?

2391
02:18:11,500 --> 02:18:13,140
You deceived your mother too?

2392
02:18:13,500 --> 02:18:15,300
Tell me. Now why are you quiet?

2393
02:18:15,420 --> 02:18:17,420
What answer will she
give you. She is crazy.

2394
02:18:17,500 --> 02:18:19,060
Yes, mad.
- Mad.

2395
02:18:19,180 --> 02:18:20,260
Absolutely insane.

2396
02:18:20,380 --> 02:18:23,140
Stop this nonsense.
Who is mad? Gauri is mad?

2397
02:18:23,580 --> 02:18:24,700
I will say all of you
are mad to think that..

2398
02:18:24,780 --> 02:18:26,820
..I am a son of a millionaire.

2399
02:18:27,060 --> 02:18:28,700
Did anyone of you try
to find out whether..

2400
02:18:28,780 --> 02:18:30,860
..this is true or false?

2401
02:18:30,980 --> 02:18:32,700
No. As soon as you
heard millionaire..

2402
02:18:32,780 --> 02:18:35,340
..you all started
hovering around me.

2403
02:18:35,700 --> 02:18:39,220
You all started
serving me and buttering me.

2404
02:18:39,500 --> 02:18:41,060
Till now, you all
would humiliate me.

2405
02:18:41,180 --> 02:18:44,500
But today, all
started respecting me.

2406
02:18:45,380 --> 02:18:47,940
Now, look at her. 'Madam sweet'.

2407
02:18:48,700 --> 02:18:50,700
All of a sudden, she
started loving me.

2408
02:18:50,820 --> 02:18:52,260
She started feeding me sweets.

2409
02:18:52,580 --> 02:18:55,580
Looking into my eyes, oh,
I am feeling shy.

2410
02:18:55,940 --> 02:18:58,700
And Mother, suddenly
you started feeling..

2411
02:18:58,780 --> 02:19:01,940
..very affectionate towards me.

2412
02:19:02,340 --> 02:19:03,900
And you brother.

2413
02:19:04,020 --> 02:19:05,420
You are a very fine man.

2414
02:19:05,780 --> 02:19:08,020
You would laugh at
whatever I would say, isn't it?

2415
02:19:08,100 --> 02:19:10,940
And you madam, you
would look after my health.

2416
02:19:11,060 --> 02:19:12,340
"Drink Horlicks. Horlicks."

2417
02:19:12,700 --> 02:19:15,740
I say not Gauri, but
all of you are mad.

2418
02:19:16,300 --> 02:19:18,380
You all are insane and selfish.

2419
02:19:19,100 --> 02:19:20,700
You all have screamed and shouted..

2420
02:19:20,780 --> 02:19:22,740
..and called Gauri as mad.

2421
02:19:22,940 --> 02:19:24,700
And Gauri has proved that you
all are mad without saying..

2422
02:19:24,780 --> 02:19:26,460
..anything and keeping silent.

2423
02:19:26,580 --> 02:19:28,140
Now, tell me. Who is mad?

2424
02:19:28,260 --> 02:19:30,260
You all are mad or
Gauri is mad? Tell me.

2425
02:19:32,180 --> 02:19:33,420
Very good, Bhola, very good.

2426
02:19:33,580 --> 02:19:34,700
You are great.

2427
02:19:35,180 --> 02:19:38,460
Bhola, you have shown us
very nicely how crazy we were.

2428
02:19:39,700 --> 02:19:42,940
You all are still here? Go. Go.

2429
02:19:50,100 --> 02:19:52,140
Father. Father.

2430
02:19:54,860 --> 02:19:56,740
Jeevan. My dear, what is the matter?

2431
02:19:57,180 --> 02:19:59,740
Father, forget whatever
has happened in the past.

2432
02:20:00,260 --> 02:20:01,500
Actually it was our mistake.

2433
02:20:01,860 --> 02:20:03,300
We used to think that Gauri is mad..

2434
02:20:03,700 --> 02:20:04,940
..but in reality we
turned out to be fools.

2435
02:20:05,580 --> 02:20:08,180
Father, now, I am
ready to marry Gauri.

2436
02:20:08,300 --> 02:20:10,740
My dear, whatever you are saying,
is that the truth?

2437
02:20:11,100 --> 02:20:12,300
My dear, say it once again.

2438
02:20:12,420 --> 02:20:15,300
Look here, whatever I say,
I say it only once.

2439
02:20:15,380 --> 02:20:16,460
And I say it very clearly.

2440
02:20:16,580 --> 02:20:17,700
Then my dear, why are
you standing outside?

2441
02:20:17,780 --> 02:20:19,140
Come in and have a cup of tea.

2442
02:20:19,260 --> 02:20:21,820
Forget tea, we will straight
away have the wedding feast.

2443
02:20:21,940 --> 02:20:23,020
You start the wedding preparations.

2444
02:20:23,500 --> 02:20:26,700
But my dear..
- No, no. You should not utter..

2445
02:20:26,780 --> 02:20:28,740
..a single word about dowry.

2446
02:20:29,100 --> 02:20:30,180
Okay, Father.

2447
02:20:41,380 --> 02:20:43,700
Bhola. Bhola. My dear,
I have come here to..

2448
02:20:43,780 --> 02:20:45,700
..give you a good news.

2449
02:20:46,300 --> 02:20:48,580
Jeevan is ready to marry Gauri now.

2450
02:20:48,900 --> 02:20:50,940
Yes my dear, and you
are responsible for that.

2451
02:20:51,140 --> 02:20:53,700
Because you proved in
front of everyone that..

2452
02:20:53,780 --> 02:20:57,060
..my Gauri is not insane
but she is absolutely sane.

2453
02:20:57,500 --> 02:20:59,700
My dear, today because of you..

2454
02:20:59,780 --> 02:21:01,220
..Gauri is going
to start a new life.

2455
02:21:01,700 --> 02:21:03,380
She is going to start
a new life, my dear.

2456
02:21:04,180 --> 02:21:07,700
Bhola, you are not an
ordinary man for us..

2457
02:21:07,780 --> 02:21:09,220
..but you are a messiah.

2458
02:21:09,460 --> 02:21:10,980
May God bless you, my dear.

2459
02:21:11,260 --> 02:21:12,340
May he always keep you happy.

2460
02:21:21,500 --> 02:21:24,940
My dear, did you hear,
Jeevan is ready to marry you.

2461
02:21:25,100 --> 02:21:26,180
He came here himself.

2462
02:21:26,340 --> 02:21:27,940
I felt so relieved.

2463
02:21:29,260 --> 02:21:30,460
Why are you laughing?

2464
02:21:30,740 --> 02:21:33,260
You felt relieved and I am restless.

2465
02:21:33,380 --> 02:21:34,580
What nonsense are you talking?

2466
02:21:34,740 --> 02:21:37,460
Mother, do not shout. If I
marry I will marry only Bhola.

2467
02:21:37,580 --> 02:21:40,260
What? What did you say?
Say it again?

2468
02:21:40,340 --> 02:21:41,460
I will beat you up.

2469
02:21:41,580 --> 02:21:43,060
Mother. What do you want?

2470
02:21:43,340 --> 02:21:45,340
Listen. Are you listening?

2471
02:21:45,700 --> 02:21:48,100
Are you listening to me?
- Yes, tell me.

2472
02:21:48,220 --> 02:21:51,020
Gauri is creating new problems.
- Problems?

2473
02:21:51,140 --> 02:21:53,780
She says she will marry only Bhola.

2474
02:21:53,860 --> 02:21:54,940
When I tried to
make her understand..

2475
02:21:55,020 --> 02:21:56,100
..she took the utensil in her hand.

2476
02:21:56,580 --> 02:21:58,860
No, one way what she
says is also right.

2477
02:21:59,900 --> 02:22:01,380
Why don't we get
her married to Bhola?

2478
02:22:01,500 --> 02:22:03,060
Have you too gone crazy?

2479
02:22:03,740 --> 02:22:06,580
Can you compare Jeevan with Bhola?

2480
02:22:06,740 --> 02:22:09,140
He has a good job, a good salary.

2481
02:22:09,260 --> 02:22:10,940
Why do you want to
reject a good proposal?

2482
02:22:11,060 --> 02:22:13,700
Do not worry, I will meet
Bhola and I will tell him..

2483
02:22:13,780 --> 02:22:14,980
..to explain everything to Gauri.

2484
02:22:15,100 --> 02:22:16,180
This is right.

2485
02:22:16,700 --> 02:22:22,740
"Come, my melodies are
calling out to you."

2486
02:22:23,500 --> 02:22:26,460
"My melodies."

2487
02:22:26,860 --> 02:22:29,140
Till today, I would sing
songs and call out to you.

2488
02:22:29,580 --> 02:22:30,700
But today you.. you..

2489
02:22:31,180 --> 02:22:34,780
Yes, Gauri. Today, I sang
a song to call out to you.

2490
02:22:35,420 --> 02:22:36,820
Because today is a
day to make decisions.

2491
02:22:37,140 --> 02:22:39,220
I too was waiting for this day.

2492
02:22:39,820 --> 02:22:41,140
Today, I am very happy.

2493
02:22:41,500 --> 02:22:43,420
I am very happy that you have
decided to come to a decision.

2494
02:22:46,980 --> 02:22:49,260
Gauri, take this, bangles.

2495
02:22:49,460 --> 02:22:53,060
Oh. Bangles. I love bangles a lot.

2496
02:22:53,500 --> 02:22:54,740
And this rose flower.

2497
02:22:55,180 --> 02:22:56,820
Which smiles like you.

2498
02:22:57,980 --> 02:22:59,260
I love this too a lot.

2499
02:23:00,380 --> 02:23:02,380
Bhola, you only pin this in my hair.

2500
02:23:03,340 --> 02:23:05,700
What is the matter today? Today,
you have brought..

2501
02:23:05,780 --> 02:23:07,180
..all those things
that I love a lot.

2502
02:23:07,940 --> 02:23:13,180
Gauri. Gauri, I wish that
you look very, very beautiful.

2503
02:23:13,700 --> 02:23:15,700
Why Bhola? Why is that?

2504
02:23:16,100 --> 02:23:19,340
Because it's our last meeting today.

2505
02:23:21,220 --> 02:23:24,700
Gauri, forget me forever.

2506
02:23:25,820 --> 02:23:27,180
You forget our love.

2507
02:23:27,340 --> 02:23:29,180
Bhola. What are you saying?

2508
02:23:29,580 --> 02:23:33,780
Gauri, our love
forcibly brought us together.

2509
02:23:34,580 --> 02:23:37,220
But now.. it is time for separation.

2510
02:23:37,420 --> 02:23:40,140
Separation. How could you say that?

2511
02:23:40,500 --> 02:23:43,900
Because I have a habit
of facing disappointment.

2512
02:23:45,020 --> 02:23:49,140
My dreams get shattered
before they are fulfilled.

2513
02:23:49,340 --> 02:23:50,700
Bhola, I do not like these words..

2514
02:23:50,780 --> 02:23:52,900
..of disappointment and dejection.

2515
02:23:53,020 --> 02:23:56,380
But what your father
thinks that is good.

2516
02:23:57,500 --> 02:24:01,020
Jeevan has a good job.
He earns a good salary.

2517
02:24:01,820 --> 02:24:03,900
He can give you all
the luxuries of life.

2518
02:24:04,700 --> 02:24:05,780
What can I give you?

2519
02:24:06,580 --> 02:24:09,100
For me, it is difficult to
earn even a one time meal.

2520
02:24:09,260 --> 02:24:10,700
Just because my father said..

2521
02:24:10,780 --> 02:24:13,420
..you are talking
to me so ruthlessly?

2522
02:24:13,980 --> 02:24:16,140
Gauri, shall I say something?
- Tell me.

2523
02:24:16,460 --> 02:24:17,700
In the battle between
the good and the bad..

2524
02:24:17,780 --> 02:24:19,940
..the good always
emerges victorious.

2525
02:24:20,300 --> 02:24:23,580
In true and false, the
truth is the winner.

2526
02:24:24,340 --> 02:24:25,700
But in the battle
between love and hunger..

2527
02:24:25,780 --> 02:24:28,340
..the hunger always is victorious.

2528
02:24:29,980 --> 02:24:31,900
The one who has fed me till today.

2529
02:24:32,860 --> 02:24:34,700
If he comes in
front of me and begs..

2530
02:24:34,780 --> 02:24:36,500
..then how can I refuse him?

2531
02:24:37,180 --> 02:24:39,580
It is my duty to
fulfil your father's wishes.

2532
02:24:40,580 --> 02:24:44,340
Gauri, forget me. I beg
of you, please forget me.

2533
02:24:44,500 --> 02:24:45,580
How can I forget you?

2534
02:24:46,100 --> 02:24:51,140
You were the one to save me
from humiliation and disgrace.

2535
02:24:51,700 --> 02:24:55,140
I saved you, that is why I
should desire to marry you?

2536
02:24:55,940 --> 02:24:57,140
How can that be possible?

2537
02:24:57,860 --> 02:25:00,700
A bridge on a river
helps a traveller to..

2538
02:25:00,780 --> 02:25:05,340
..cross on the other side,
but he stays where he is.

2539
02:25:06,100 --> 02:25:10,340
He cannot desire to go along with
the traveller on the other side.

2540
02:25:10,580 --> 02:25:12,020
Is this your final decision?

2541
02:25:12,220 --> 02:25:15,580
Yes, Gauri, I am going to
Delhi in search of a job.

2542
02:25:16,140 --> 02:25:19,700
You marry Jeevan and
live a happy life.

2543
02:25:20,260 --> 02:25:23,460
Okay, then you too will
have to promise me one thing.

2544
02:25:23,700 --> 02:25:27,700
What? Only that I too
should marry some girl..

2545
02:25:27,780 --> 02:25:29,700
..and settle down in life?

2546
02:25:29,860 --> 02:25:33,700
No, Bhola. No. If I am
compelled to forget you..

2547
02:25:33,780 --> 02:25:35,260
..even then you do not forget me.

2548
02:25:36,140 --> 02:25:37,700
The place that you have
for me in your heart..

2549
02:25:37,780 --> 02:25:42,220
..no other girl can take
that place. Never, Bhola, never.

2550
02:25:55,980 --> 02:25:57,700
Hey, did you listen?
- What is it?

2551
02:25:58,100 --> 02:25:59,180
Come here.

2552
02:25:59,980 --> 02:26:02,700
Aunt Leela is very smart.
She is quietly getting Gauri..

2553
02:26:02,780 --> 02:26:04,060
..married to Jeevan.

2554
02:26:04,260 --> 02:26:05,940
Look, an invitation card.

2555
02:26:06,060 --> 02:26:07,420
Wedding.
- Yes. - Let it be. Let it be.

2556
02:26:07,740 --> 02:26:09,300
But have you noticed something?
- What?

2557
02:26:09,420 --> 02:26:10,700
For the first time, there is
a wedding in this shanty..

2558
02:26:10,780 --> 02:26:12,940
..and Bhola is not here,
he has gone to Delhi.

2559
02:26:13,380 --> 02:26:14,900
You do not
understand such a small thing?

2560
02:26:15,140 --> 02:26:16,700
Aunt was waiting for
this moment when Bhola..

2561
02:26:16,780 --> 02:26:19,580
..goes from here and
she gets Gauri married.

2562
02:26:19,700 --> 02:26:21,340
Really?
- Yes. - But why?

2563
02:26:21,500 --> 02:26:25,100
Looks like there was some
affair between Bhola and Gauri.

2564
02:26:25,260 --> 02:26:26,740
Affair?
- Yes. - Oh, my God.

2565
02:26:26,860 --> 02:26:30,140
Hey, talk softly. Whether
there was an affair or not.

2566
02:26:30,220 --> 02:26:31,340
What have we got to do with that?

2567
02:26:31,460 --> 02:26:33,940
I am worried what gift
should we give in this wedding.

2568
02:26:34,340 --> 02:26:39,500
Idea. Like a gift, we will keep
Pappu for a while on their lap.

2569
02:26:39,580 --> 02:26:40,820
That is fine.
- That is done?

2570
02:26:41,020 --> 02:26:43,780
Jaya, I am seriously
worried and you are joking.

2571
02:26:43,900 --> 02:26:45,900
Okay, do this..
- Yes, tell me what to do?

2572
02:26:46,220 --> 02:26:49,500
You do not attend the
wedding and do not sing there.

2573
02:26:49,700 --> 02:26:51,500
That will be your biggest present.

2574
02:26:51,580 --> 02:26:52,780
Understood. Understood.

2575
02:26:57,220 --> 02:26:58,300
Bring the bride.

2576
02:26:58,700 --> 02:26:59,780
I will get her immediately.

2577
02:27:00,420 --> 02:27:01,700
Jaya.
- What?

2578
02:27:01,780 --> 02:27:05,340
Looking at this ambience,
I remembered our wedding.

2579
02:27:06,100 --> 02:27:09,060
You would look so beautiful then?
- And now?

2580
02:27:09,180 --> 02:27:12,300
Now? Now too you look beautiful.
- Yes.

2581
02:27:12,380 --> 02:27:13,460
Be careful.

2582
02:27:20,020 --> 02:27:24,420
Sit down.
- I want some water.

2583
02:27:26,420 --> 02:27:27,780
Someone please get water.

2584
02:27:28,700 --> 02:27:29,780
Quickly.

2585
02:27:35,820 --> 02:27:36,940
Yes, now, sit down.

2586
02:27:53,340 --> 02:27:55,860
Groom, get up.

2587
02:27:57,980 --> 02:27:59,180
I say get up.

2588
02:28:01,300 --> 02:28:02,380
What nonsense is this?

2589
02:28:02,500 --> 02:28:03,580
Father, what is all this?

2590
02:28:03,740 --> 02:28:05,700
Gauri, my dear, what is all this?

2591
02:28:07,420 --> 02:28:09,820
I want to talk to the groom.

2592
02:28:10,340 --> 02:28:12,700
Why you? That day you
called me crazy and demanded..

2593
02:28:12,780 --> 02:28:14,380
..Rs.15000, isn't it?

2594
02:28:14,740 --> 02:28:15,820
But now where am I
demanding any money?

2595
02:28:16,020 --> 02:28:17,140
At that time you
had demanded or not?

2596
02:28:17,500 --> 02:28:18,780
Yes, yes, I had demanded, so what?

2597
02:28:19,340 --> 02:28:21,700
But if you would have
said that this girl is mad..

2598
02:28:21,780 --> 02:28:23,420
..I will not marry you..

2599
02:28:23,820 --> 02:28:25,260
Then I would have
accepted you as a decent man.

2600
02:28:25,500 --> 02:28:27,700
But you.. if at that time
we would have given you..

2601
02:28:27,780 --> 02:28:30,820
..Rs.15000, you were
ready to marry a mad girl.

2602
02:28:30,980 --> 02:28:33,060
You are mad. Mad after money.

2603
02:28:33,260 --> 02:28:35,700
Now, I say that if
you give me Rs.15000..

2604
02:28:35,780 --> 02:28:37,460
..only then will I marry you.

2605
02:28:37,580 --> 02:28:40,260
What did you say? - Tell me, are
you willing to give me Rs.15000?

2606
02:28:40,380 --> 02:28:43,140
Great. Tit for tat.

2607
02:28:43,260 --> 02:28:45,740
Dear Gauri, what are you doing?

2608
02:28:46,500 --> 02:28:48,580
No one should interfere between us.

2609
02:28:48,860 --> 02:28:50,940
Tell me, are you
willing to marry me?

2610
02:28:51,060 --> 02:28:52,580
This is not a wedding,
this is disaster.

2611
02:28:52,860 --> 02:28:53,940
This is my insult.

2612
02:28:54,180 --> 02:28:55,940
I will definitely
avenge my humiliation.

2613
02:28:57,100 --> 02:28:59,420
Father. Why are you
reading the paper?

2614
02:28:59,500 --> 02:29:00,860
Just see what is going on here.

2615
02:29:01,020 --> 02:29:02,780
The wedding is over? Come,
we will go to have food.

2616
02:29:02,900 --> 02:29:06,460
Not to eat food, but
we are humiliated.

2617
02:29:06,580 --> 02:29:08,580
What did you say, we are humiliated?

2618
02:29:08,860 --> 02:29:11,740
Mr. Dindayal, I will
file a defamation suit.

2619
02:29:11,860 --> 02:29:16,260
And I will take my revenge.
I will not spare them.

2620
02:29:16,700 --> 02:29:20,940
Mr. Makhan Lal, file a
defamation case later.

2621
02:29:21,260 --> 02:29:24,300
First, teach your son and
daughter to speak properly.

2622
02:29:24,420 --> 02:29:27,940
And take what is left
and go away from here.

2623
02:29:28,100 --> 02:29:29,340
Why are all of you standing here?

2624
02:29:29,420 --> 02:29:30,500
The marriage is not
going to take place.

2625
02:29:30,580 --> 02:29:31,780
Go.
- Hey, all of you, listen, listen.

2626
02:29:31,860 --> 02:29:33,100
Wait all of you.

2627
02:29:33,700 --> 02:29:36,700
Till today, you must have
only heard the stories of..

2628
02:29:36,780 --> 02:29:38,940
..the bravery of Indian girls.

2629
02:29:39,140 --> 02:29:40,860
You must have read them in books.

2630
02:29:41,020 --> 02:29:43,700
But today, see it yourselves..

2631
02:29:43,780 --> 02:29:45,060
Well done, my dear.

2632
02:29:45,180 --> 02:29:46,500
Enough. Enough. That is enough now.

2633
02:29:46,580 --> 02:29:48,260
Come on, Father. And
all of you too go home.

2634
02:29:48,340 --> 02:29:50,860
Yes, yes, all of you
go from here. Come on.

2635
02:29:52,860 --> 02:29:55,460
My dear Gauri, what have you done?

2636
02:29:56,940 --> 02:29:58,260
What have you done?

2637
02:29:59,060 --> 02:30:02,700
Father, why are you
looking at me like this?

2638
02:30:03,220 --> 02:30:06,020
Or are you thinking that
I have again gone crazy?

2639
02:30:06,900 --> 02:30:11,300
No, Father, I am fine.
I am absolutely fine.

2640
02:30:11,740 --> 02:30:13,700
My dear, all that you have done..

2641
02:30:13,780 --> 02:30:15,460
..you have done it in your sanity.

2642
02:30:15,940 --> 02:30:20,420
Yes father, to teach
these greedy people a lesson.

2643
02:30:21,220 --> 02:30:22,700
Isn't it right?
- Yes, my dear.

2644
02:30:23,300 --> 02:30:25,820
I already had a
certificate of being insane.

2645
02:30:26,500 --> 02:30:27,700
By acting like an insane person..

2646
02:30:27,780 --> 02:30:30,220
..I have taught
all of them a lesson.

2647
02:30:30,740 --> 02:30:33,380
I.. Did I make any mistake?

2648
02:30:33,500 --> 02:30:35,780
No, my dear. You have
not committed any mistake.

2649
02:30:36,460 --> 02:30:38,140
My dear, you have not
committed any mistake.

2650
02:30:41,340 --> 02:30:44,220
Father, do not beat me.
- What are you doing? Stop this.

2651
02:30:44,420 --> 02:30:46,700
You are raising your
hand on your daughter?

2652
02:30:46,980 --> 02:30:48,060
Are you in your senses?

2653
02:30:48,180 --> 02:30:49,580
Sher Singh, I am in my senses.

2654
02:30:49,740 --> 02:30:51,700
But it is better if
a girl like her dies.

2655
02:30:52,220 --> 02:30:54,820
I have suffered so
many difficulties for her.

2656
02:30:55,220 --> 02:30:58,060
She has become a burden for me.

2657
02:30:58,740 --> 02:31:01,340
Just because I am her father,
I am tolerating all this.

2658
02:31:01,460 --> 02:31:04,740
You do not forget what all
our girls have to suffer.

2659
02:31:05,380 --> 02:31:09,780
Whatever sorrows come their way,
they quietly bear it.

2660
02:31:10,100 --> 02:31:11,380
I saw her love.

2661
02:31:11,940 --> 02:31:14,740
She loves her
principles more than her father.

2662
02:31:15,300 --> 02:31:17,700
I am telling you the
truth the day she dies..

2663
02:31:17,780 --> 02:31:19,500
..I will live peacefully.

2664
02:31:19,580 --> 02:31:20,740
You wretched girl.

2665
02:31:21,700 --> 02:31:23,420
Now, I will not allow you
to raise your hand on her.

2666
02:31:24,020 --> 02:31:26,700
If she is a burden for
you then I am willing to..

2667
02:31:26,780 --> 02:31:28,300
..shoulder her burden.

2668
02:31:29,700 --> 02:31:31,220
I will make her tie Rakhi (thread
symbolising brother-sister bond).

2669
02:31:31,500 --> 02:31:32,860
I will make her my sister.

2670
02:31:32,980 --> 02:31:34,780
Sher Singh.
- Yes, Manohar Lal.

2671
02:31:35,780 --> 02:31:37,940
Your daughter is very fortunate.

2672
02:31:38,780 --> 02:31:42,060
I will get my sister
married in some wealthy family.

2673
02:31:42,340 --> 02:31:43,420
I will get her
married to some prince.

2674
02:31:44,020 --> 02:31:46,380
You all could not
understand my Bhola.

2675
02:31:46,460 --> 02:31:47,900
You thought he was useless.

2676
02:31:48,060 --> 02:31:49,940
Now, you just watch.
He has gone to Delhi.

2677
02:31:50,020 --> 02:31:51,340
He will return as
a renowned officer.

2678
02:31:51,500 --> 02:31:54,980
And now, whatever you say I will
get my sister married to Bhola.

2679
02:31:56,300 --> 02:31:58,700
Sher Singh, till today, we would..

2680
02:31:58,780 --> 02:32:01,820
..bow down in
front of your strength.

2681
02:32:02,420 --> 02:32:06,260
And today, we bow down in
front of your intelligence.

2682
02:32:06,500 --> 02:32:08,900
Brother, please do not embarrass me.

2683
02:32:09,180 --> 02:32:10,780
I am a simple human being.

2684
02:32:11,060 --> 02:32:12,780
My intelligence is like me.

2685
02:32:12,940 --> 02:32:14,900
Sher Singh.
- And you do not worry.

2686
02:32:15,020 --> 02:32:17,900
Just watch in what
stately way my boy will return.

2687
02:32:18,940 --> 02:32:20,020
Bhola has come.

2688
02:32:21,100 --> 02:32:22,580
Everyone's Bhola has come.

2689
02:32:22,700 --> 02:32:24,300
Brother, Bhola has come.

2690
02:32:24,420 --> 02:32:26,820
Bhola come, you have a
very long life, come.

2691
02:32:29,260 --> 02:32:31,500
Bhola.
- Mother. - My Bhola has come.

2692
02:32:31,580 --> 02:32:33,300
Hey, Bhola, it is you?
- Are you fine?

2693
02:32:33,420 --> 02:32:34,700
Just see his personality.

2694
02:32:35,500 --> 02:32:36,860
Father.
- God bless you.

2695
02:32:37,260 --> 02:32:39,220
Hey, Bhola.
- Brother.

2696
02:32:39,860 --> 02:32:41,220
My brave lad has returned.

2697
02:32:41,580 --> 02:32:43,940
Oh, Bhola, what is your salary?

2698
02:32:44,060 --> 02:32:45,140
Rs.1000.

2699
02:32:45,260 --> 02:32:46,820
What? Ten hundred rupee notes?

2700
02:32:46,940 --> 02:32:48,500
Not for a year but for a month.

2701
02:32:48,580 --> 02:32:50,940
Great. Great. He is a brave lad.

2702
02:32:51,060 --> 02:32:52,700
Bhola, what are you
looking here and there?

2703
02:32:52,860 --> 02:32:55,340
I was looking out for Gauri, it's
Gauri's wedding today, isn't it?

2704
02:32:55,580 --> 02:32:57,100
I have brought a gift for her.

2705
02:32:57,260 --> 02:32:59,100
I will give her this
gift in front of you all.

2706
02:32:59,220 --> 02:33:01,940
Wait. Are you going to give a gift?

2707
02:33:02,580 --> 02:33:03,700
Come, Sister, come.

2708
02:33:05,700 --> 02:33:09,180
Before you give a gift,
I will give you a gift.

2709
02:33:09,420 --> 02:33:11,740
Brother, what
happened to Gauri's wedding?

2710
02:33:11,900 --> 02:33:13,460
Like the engagement, the
wedding too is broken.

2711
02:33:13,580 --> 02:33:16,700
What? - Bhola, I want to be
relieved of my responsibility..

2712
02:33:16,780 --> 02:33:19,700
..after handing over the
possession to the rightful person.

2713
02:33:19,780 --> 02:33:20,980
Take her, take care of her.

2714
02:33:21,260 --> 02:33:24,580
No, Brother. You are
putting me in a dilemma.

2715
02:33:24,940 --> 02:33:26,220
Hey, what dilemma?

2716
02:33:26,740 --> 02:33:28,260
There I got married to a girl.

2717
02:33:28,500 --> 02:33:29,580
Registered marriage.

2718
02:33:32,260 --> 02:33:36,140
Bhola, you took my advice
to fall in love with her.

2719
02:33:36,500 --> 02:33:37,780
And you fell in love with her.

2720
02:33:38,300 --> 02:33:40,500
And now, you have become a
renowned officer in Delhi.

2721
02:33:40,860 --> 02:33:43,220
After earning so much money,
you forgot your love.

2722
02:33:43,420 --> 02:33:44,500
Shame on you.

2723
02:33:44,700 --> 02:33:47,140
Brother, you are
misunderstanding me.

2724
02:33:47,940 --> 02:33:53,700
Bhola, I had told you that the
place that is created for me..

2725
02:33:53,780 --> 02:33:55,940
..will not be taken
by any other girl.

2726
02:33:56,060 --> 02:33:57,380
I had told you that, isn't it?

2727
02:33:57,500 --> 02:33:59,140
Yes, Gauri, you had told me that.

2728
02:33:59,700 --> 02:34:01,300
But you had not told me in this way.

2729
02:34:02,380 --> 02:34:05,580
Listen, Gauri, whatever
had to happen has happened.

2730
02:34:05,900 --> 02:34:07,980
Now, all of you please forgive me.

2731
02:34:08,460 --> 02:34:10,700
Mother, please accept
my happiness as yours.

2732
02:34:10,860 --> 02:34:13,780
Father, please bless me and my wife.

2733
02:34:14,260 --> 02:34:15,340
She has come along with me.

2734
02:34:16,340 --> 02:34:17,420
Listen.

2735
02:34:19,500 --> 02:34:21,020
Pushpa, come.

2736
02:34:22,900 --> 02:34:24,700
This is our family.

2737
02:34:25,020 --> 02:34:26,140
Take father's blessings.

2738
02:34:27,420 --> 02:34:29,220
Do not feel shy,
Pushpa. Take his blessings.

2739
02:34:29,700 --> 02:34:31,460
What nonsense is this?
Take his blessings.

2740
02:34:31,900 --> 02:34:33,060
I am Vivek.

2741
02:34:35,340 --> 02:34:36,980
Bhola, you are great.

2742
02:34:37,420 --> 02:34:40,940
Your mischief has stunned all of us.

2743
02:34:41,100 --> 02:34:42,500
You rogue.

2744
02:34:42,580 --> 02:34:45,140
Brother, there you said it.
Now, you gave me your blessings.

2745
02:34:45,260 --> 02:34:48,100
To hear the word
'rogue' I did this drama.

2746
02:34:48,220 --> 02:34:51,700
You! - No, no..

2747
02:34:52,340 --> 02:34:54,220
This blessing is for one thing.

2748
02:34:54,300 --> 02:34:55,500
But I will give you
many blessings like these.

2749
02:34:55,580 --> 02:35:00,140
You rogue. You rogue. You rogue.

2750
02:35:00,700 --> 02:35:02,420
Come on, now,
quickly sit on the dais..

2751
02:35:02,500 --> 02:35:04,060
..otherwise the
auspicious time will pass away.

2752
02:35:04,180 --> 02:35:06,460
No, Brother, I will not
go on to the dais. - Why?

2753
02:35:06,740 --> 02:35:09,220
If Bhola gets married then
that will be under the staircase..

2754
02:35:09,340 --> 02:35:10,780
Hey. Under the staircase?

2755
02:35:10,940 --> 02:35:12,140
Okay, as you wish.

2756
02:35:12,220 --> 02:35:13,820
What do I care!

2757
